                            <h1 class="bebas-neue guide-dog-raisers-header-h1">Mass Communications MA Student Brings Lone Star Guide Dog Raisers to Lubbock</h1>

                            <p><em><small>by Rachel Blevins, photos courtesy Kaitlyn Beckert</small></em></p>
